room_title: Escape room "Sunken Submarine Tour" by Key To Escape in Nashua
review: My family of four (11 yrs and 14 yrs old kids) went on Sunday and did the Submarine room at the challenging level. It was a lot of fun and the hour flew by. We did finally escape and can't wait to go back and try a different room! Very friendly staff as well.

room_title: Escape room "Sunken Submarine Tour" by Key To Escape in Nashua
review: The submarine room was incredibly creative, fun and challenging! Escaped with barely 2 minutes left and had such a great time solving the puzzles. Already planning to come back as soon as the next room is open!

room_title: Escape room "Sunken Submarine Tour" by Key To Escape in Nashua
review: We did the submarine room, it was a great challenge with different problems/puzzles than we've seen before. I definitely recommend Key to Escape!
